OL,3,CProvisional trial date set for
OL,4,CHorncastle murder case
OL,6,FA man charged with murdering a 27-year-
OL,7,Fold woman at a property in
OL,8,FLincolnshire could face trial later
OL,9,Fthis year.
OL,11,FKhyali Jana Rahim Bad Shah died after
OL,12,Fan incident at Warwickshires Way,
OL,13,FHorncastle, on Thursday 2 April.
OL,15,FMohammad Raees Mohammad Rahim, 34, of
OL,16,FWarwickshires Way, was due to appear
OL,17,Fat Lincoln Crown Court on Wednesday
OL,18,Fcharged with her murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
