OL,3,CProvisional trial date set for
OL,4,CHorncastle murder case
OL,6,FHe was not produced from custody and
OL,7,FJudge Simon Hirst adjourned the case
OL,8,Ffor a plea and trial preparation
OL,9,Fhearing at the same court on 15 May.
OL,11,FThe case was listed for a provisional
OL,12,Ftrial on 5 October.
OL,14,FMr Rahim was remanded into custody
OL,15,Funtil his next court appearance.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
